snippet: The police are still investigating whether bullying played any role in a Staten Island girl’s suicide.
abstract: New York City Police Dept says that it is still investigating whether bullying played any role in the suicide of 15-year-old Staten Island high school student Amanda Cummings.
lead_paragraph: The police are still investigating whether bullying played any role in a Staten Island girl’s suicide.

headline.seo: Bullying Examined in Staten Island Girl’s Suicide
headline.main: Bullying Not Yet Ruled Out in a Suicide
